_EOE_jellomizer
Having done work for the State of NY, I am sure this happens else where.Fair and Competitive bidding work like this...You need a job to be done.You call the guys who you want to do it.They do some "Free" analysis of the problem.They give you the requirements as they would do it.They also attach the Resume of the people who they want to do the work.They make the bids to match the requirements and fit the resume of the people.They take in all the bid.Then they find the winning bid which isn't the cheapest but is a perfect match to the requirements.
which happens to be the company that did the free analysis
