I just happened to go through "Government contracts" training nd what you describe is illegal, punishable by up to 5 years in prison for the official giving the info to would be contractors and whoever got the info + up to 50.000 in fines from persons and up to 500.000 from the corporation that improperly obtained such contract + damages and stuff.The rule is if you write specs, you cannot bid.If you leak exact specs or bid details to participating bidders you get fined and go to jail.
there are total of 5 rules or so.
